verbose_text: [XREF_BIBR] Studies using molecular biology techniques revealed that ESWT upregulated the expressions of alpha-smooth muscle actin, von Willebrand factor, neuronal NO synthase, and vascular endothelial growth factor and downregulated the expression of the receptor for advanced glycation endproducts in the corpus cavernosum.
evidence: expressions of alpha-smooth muscle actin, von Willebrand factor, neuronal NO synthase, and vascular endothelial growth factor
